{"tid":198931,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(Timothy：唔打北韓了!) 侵 想凍結支持朝核的國企在美資產 <棋王中招>","createTime":"2017-04-12T22:33:51.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-12T22:33:51.000Z","uid":24547,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"790d9854da68237864430b5ca9e5ec1f3a46a159","tid":198931,"uid":24547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T22:33:51.000Z","msg":"Testing topic<br />\n日媒稱，美國政府已經向日本政府通報，正考慮對與朝鮮核武器開發有關的中國企業加大製裁。這得到了多位日美外交人士證實。特朗普政府要求對朝鮮具有影響力的中國加大壓力，稱如果中國不拿出具體行動，美國將採取&ldquo;單獨行動&rdquo;，包括凍結中國企業在美國的資產等。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://military.china.com/important/11132797/20170412/30412803.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmilitary.china.com%2Fimportant%2F11132797%2F20170412%2F30412803.html&d=lW7zubw4D25L16l94wxnCi7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=bcc5956e\" target=\"_blank\">http://military.china.com/important/11132797/20170412/30412803.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>(突發)人民幣告急：離岸匯率跌破6.90 像是要發生什麼<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/197785/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/197785/page/1</a></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n果然係商人，美國打唔打北韓根本唔係重點，重點是美國會否找搵藉口對中國嘅企業作出制裁或者凍結資產。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uazfxhg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fuazfxhg.png&h=3b9d18a9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://inews.gtimg.com/newsapp_match/0/1217138238/0\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Finews.gtimg.com%2Fnewsapp_match%2F0%2F1217138238%2F0&h=b82d8ca8&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}